    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="locations-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Locations</h2>
      <p class="intro">Our screens can be found in many popular locations throughout the midlands. Our screens offer a unique format - keeping your message in front of your customers in your location, even when other ads are playing.</p>
      
